name: HEN UNDER ATTACK!!! FEAR NOT
description: GREED,VANITY, JEALOUSY, CONFLICT OF INTERESTS, RIVALRY, HACKERS. Under current circumstances, wanted to show in one original and unique work, how situation evolves, how many artists, small ones, and medium ones, get affected by the greed of a few. They look for easy and fast cash, a lot of cash, the artist just create for survive, for share love and their dreams, so FEAR NOT, at the end, the good will always prevail. Ascii and Pixel Art mixed technique. A tribute to Pop Art. Pixel and Ascii Digital Art by MagnaK @ascii_k
